<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.8">
<l>tārkkiḷan tampik karacīntu  taṇṭakam</l>
<l>nūṟṟavaḷ colkoṇṭu pōki nuṭaṅkiṭaic</l>
<l>cūrppaṇa kāvaic ceviyoṭu mūkkava</l>
<l>ḷārkka varintāṉaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">vayōttik karacaṉaip pāṭippaṟa.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about he who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having given [his] kingdom and [his royal] garland</l>
<l rend="indent">to [his] younger brother,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] gone to the Daṇḍaka forest</l>
<l rend="indent">at the word of the scheming woman,</l>
<l>cut off the nose along with the ears of Śūrpaṇakhā,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a thin waist,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [she] howled!</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the king of Ayodhyā!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
